      "text": "وَيْلٌ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ لُّمَزَةٍۙ",
      "text_translation": "Celakalah bagi setiap pengumpat dan pencela,"
    },
    {
      "audio": "https://quran.kemenag.go.id/cmsq/source/s01/104002.mp3",
      "id": 6181,
